.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET_CLOSE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-close \- flush and close the wallet WAL
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-close
.I wallet_name
.SH DESCRIPTION
Runs WAL checkpoint to flush pending writes and close the wallet cleanly.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
